last_episode_to_air.name: There Will Be Blood
last_episode_to_air.overview: In a final battle to spare Ian and Gwen's life, Ezra faces Aniya, one-on-one. Although close, a fatal victory is won, ending with a surprise visit from the vampire council.

name: EZRA
overview: After fleeing the dark and demonic chains of his shadowy old home, Ezra, a killer gay vampire, takes a leap of faith and enters the modern world.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: Ezra, a gay vampire, takes a leap of faith and enters the modern human world. It's here he meets his best friend, Gwen, and a potential next victim.

episodes.name: Thirsty
episodes.overview: Ezra begins counseling students as part of his psychology degree. Meanwhile, the popular girl in school is on the hunt for her GBF.

episodes.name: Canceled
episodes.overview: A now ex-popular social media star, canceled for his inappropriate conduct with minors, stops by Wood Cress on his tour. Ezra, who now has a developing situation ship with Ian, sees this as a perfect opportunity for his next meal.

episodes.name: Drac-U-Nah
episodes.overview: Gwen takes Ezra to his first Halloween party, however, once there, Ezra feels a bit like he's being made fun of. In his most honest state, Ian and Ezra finally get together.

episodes.name: Pale
episodes.overview: Ezra meets the parents of his now boyfriend, Ian. Although some issues arise, everything goes much better than expected, until Aniya, Ezra's cousin, finds his whereabouts.

episodes.name: King of the Castle
episodes.overview: Aniya, the ruler of all vampires, plans to abandon her duties and run away with her love, Nathaniel. In a last ditch effort to prevent that, Kylo, Aniya's sidekick, exposes her love's infidelity.

episodes.name: Come Out Come Out
episodes.overview: When Ezra's past trauma finally starts to get to him, he tries avoiding Ian, leading them to a rocky place, while Gwen seemingly works her way into a solid one.

episodes.name: Seance
episodes.overview: Aniya enters the human world to find her cousin, Ezra, however while there, Aniya meets an unsuspecting interest. Ezra grows paranoid about his cousin's whereabouts and brings in an old friend for help.

episodes.name: Slay
episodes.overview: Ezra spirals while he searches for a solution as his cousin, Aniya, plots to murder his loved ones. Gwen's new brewing love interest, Cade, takes a moment to reveal himself to Kylo.

episodes.name: There Will Be Blood
episodes.overview: In a final battle to spare Ian and Gwen's life, Ezra faces Aniya, one-on-one. Although close, a fatal victory is won, ending with a surprise visit from the vampire council.
